{"tid":622455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於7欖草地上除褲露械 英男稱不知後果被判罰款","createTime":"2018-04-09T07:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T12:54:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c481727e76e7bec29d59f912744a662c6aa348c","tid":622455,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:04:05.000Z","msg":"香港國際七人欖球賽（7欖）在上周五至日在香港大球場上演，有來自英國的23歲售貨員在周日到場觀看賽事期間，酒後情緒高漲，上身赤裸跑到草地後脫褲向公眾露械，結果被控在公眾地方作出猥褻行為罪，今在裁判法院被罰款6,000元。<br />\n<br />\n被告MONTEITH Maximilian John Walter今於裁判法院認罪，求情指當時飲醉了，亦不知露械的後果如此嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n被告昨日在草地後脫褲向公眾露械後，已即被場內的保安捉住帶往警崗。"},{"pid":"950a5a3681044a0360822ef543a0a958d9d3acc6","tid":622455,"uid":128014,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"居然無港女衝去含幫佢手遮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條鬼佬一定好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08f49390ea755b401320a9224d81c6f7996d83c","tid":622455,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"你睇下<br />\n白鬼就係咁撚樣<br />\n如果新加坡佢咁撚樣攪法..."},{"pid":"e935b52ed8197e09ea8f9b4f923fdff79e353f0c","tid":622455,"uid":53672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"d大陸人周街屙尿點解無事"},{"pid":"0bf457593d4b1d65eb85607aa9d5846ba52b0b12","tid":622455,"uid":151013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"洋腸露械唔洗你教"},{"pid":"c55424833eaa3242662a795fa8fd337758144432","tid":622455,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70f729df9f06dd37c8ec877c13f6c3a1636d1c51","tid":622455,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm